# Installation

```
sudo apt install git

mkdir -p ~/.local/share
git clone git@github.com:mreq/dotfiles.git ~/.local/share/dotfiles

"$HOME/.local/share/dotfiles/setup/setup.sh"
"$HOME/.local/share/dotfiles/config/install.sh"

sudo ln -s "$HOME/.local/share/dotfiles/cron/clear_downloads" /etc/cron.daily/clear_downloads

sudo ln -s "$HOME/.local/share/dotfiles/cron/clear_dropbox" /etc/cron.daily/clear_dropbox

sudo ln -s "$HOME/.local/share/dotfiles/cron/clear_work_logs" /etc/cron.daily/clear_work_logs
```
